DIE Oostelike Provinsie se rugby-talent word in Junie in Kimberley ’n laaste keer bekyk voordat die onderskeie skolespanne aangewys word. Spanne is aangewys om op 9 Junie met Griekwas se spanne kragte te meet waarna die OP-spanne vir die provinsiale weke in Julie gekies sal word. Die o. 18-groepe is: Shaun Felix: Basi Malesu, (Sac), Corné Slabbert (G), Bame Malesu (Sac), Dumisa Ncovane (G), Laken Gray (G), Henri du Toit (NM), Regardt Ferreira (NM), Rubin du Pont (B), Ronaldo Pedro (G), Claude Jacobs (Marl), Joshua Oosthuizen (G), Louis du Preez (G), Lennox Holster (Marl), Liyema Matyolweni (G), Enrique Franks (G), Chris Poole (Sac), Zuki Salie (B), Wiehan Pretorius (Marl), Luan Ras (F), Arno Nel (GC), Jaco Nel (Marl), Charles Fleming (Sac), Delron Dicken (NM). Neville Botha: Ryan Windvogel (P), Yolisa Dladla (G), Shaquile Adams (G), Jarred Comley (B), Ricardo Diederick (D), Kevin Kanenunga (VP), Theo Repinz (G), Werner Louw (NM), André Gerber (F), Jeandré Liebenberg (F), Ricardo Krige (NM), Monray Potgieter (F), De-Han van Zyl (NM), Octavian Muller (B), Cedwyn Grootboom (C), Marinus Barnard (DP), William Moffatt (F), Tiaan du Toit (B), Danie van der Merwe (F), Antonio Krige (Hum), Mario Japhta (C), Shemondré Hannes (DP), Clinton Lodewyk (Wvil), Damian Ruiters (JBaai), Grayson Ditlow (F). Stegman van Zyl: Junior Mazibuko (Aliwal), Hlumelo Gumetana (Marl), Tsepang Ranto (Aliwal), Divan Nel (Volk), Matt Hillary, Dom Shone, Christiaan Roebert, Miles Dankwerts (almal Sac), Amahle Maku (Burg), Anele Mankongolo (KC), Abongile Klaas (KC), Jeandré Snyman (Marl), Ant Moore (Sac), Cole Kirkwood (MW), Ambeza Zenzile (Marl), Joop Pasque (Marl), Duppie du Preez (Winter), Ernst Mostert (Volk), Danie Naudé (Aliwal), Buhle Matshaya (Sac), Romano Fitz (GC), Sandiso Charles (KC), Semi Jack (Marl), Khali Khalipha (KC), Eldrico Kiewiets (GC). Die o. 16-groepe is: Groep A: A. Limba, S. Ndoto (albei Pearson), H. Vermaak (Grey), B. Mmile (Sac), D. Halgreen, D. Royle (albei Grey), R. du Pre